{\f1\fs20\cf6\i [Duration: ~2 minutes | Stand confident, make eye contact]\par}
\par

{\f1\fs22 Good morning / afternoon, respected panel members.\par
\par
My name is [Your Name], and I served as the Front-End Developer for our group project titled \b BusGo \emdash an Online Bus Travelling Management System\b0  designed specifically for the Sri Lankan public transport context.\par
\par
My contribution to this project spans two key technology areas:\par
\par
{\pard\li720
\b 1.\b0  A \b React-based Admin Web Panel\b0  \emdash a full-featured browser dashboard for transport administrators to manage the entire bus network in real time.\par
