\par

{\f1\fs24\b\cf3 QR Card Screen\par}
\par
{\f1\fs22 Every passenger has a unique digital QR card. This screen:\par
{\pard\li720
Fetches the user\rquote s profile from the UserProvider.\par
Generates a QR code using the passenger\rquote s unique QR code string (or falls back to a BUSGO-[userID] format).\par
Displays it as a physical-looking card with the user\rquote s name and ID, ready to be scanned by the conductor.\par
\par}
