{\f1\fs24\b\cf3 Emergency Screen\par}
\par
{\f1\fs22 Passengers can submit an emergency report from within the app. The screen presents categorised emergency type buttons and an optional free-text details field. Submissions are sent to the backend where they become visible to administrators on the Emergency Management page immediately.\par
