{\f1\fs28\b\cf2 5.4 BusGo Scanner \emdash Ticket Scanner App\par}
\par
{\f1\fs22 The Scanner app is used by bus conductors to validate passenger QR tickets. It is the most focused of the three mobile apps, with a single primary function.\par
}
\par

{\f1\fs24\b\cf3 Active Scanner Screen\par}
\par
{\f1\fs22 This is the heart of the scanner app:\par
{\pard\li720
\b Animated scanning viewfinder:\b0  I implemented a custom animated viewfinder using two AnimationControllers. A \b scan line\b0  moves up and down continuously through the camera frame, and the viewfinder frame itself \b pulses\b0  rhythmically, both implemented with looping Tween animations and CurvedAnimation easing. This provides visual feedback that the scanner is active and looking for a QR code.\par
