\b Bottom info panel:\b0  Shows instructions and the scanner\rquote s status.\par
\par}
}
\par

{\f1\fs24\b\cf3 Scan Result Screens\par}
\par
{\f1\fs22 {\pard\li720
\b Scan Success Screen:\b0  Shown when a valid QR code is detected. Displays the passenger\rquote s name, ticket information, and a green confirmation UI.\par
\b Scan Error Screen:\b0  Shown when an invalid or expired QR code is detected, with a clear error message and a retry button.\par
\par}
}
